年度偵字第 29810號    110年10月14日22時14分許 網路匯款 5萬元","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDM/111%2c%e5%8e%9f%e9%87%91%e8%a8%b4%2c59%2c20221102%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDM,111,原金訴,59,20221102,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"原金訴","JNO":"59","JDATE":"20221102","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}